        {
            "title": "聯儲會Kashkari稱不支持上次降息 尚未就12月會議拿定主意",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"明尼阿波利斯联邦储备银行行长Neel Kashkari\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gG.F7YbnMUfGWYFbg8.52A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/4d25c9298dc90d6ff2c9ebc74d1bf839\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">明尼阿波利斯联邦储备银行行长<span>Neel Kashkari</span></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 明尼阿波利斯聯邦儲備銀行行長Neel Kashkari表示，他不支持聯儲會上一次的降息決定，但對12月的政策會議應採取何種行動仍未作出決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「來自市場反饋和數據的跡象都顯示，經濟活動的潛在韌性超出我的預期，」Kashkari周四接受彭博新聞社採訪時表示。他說，這表明聯儲會在10月會議上應暫停降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kashkari表示，此後公佈的數據顯示經濟形勢「基本保持不變」。至於即將到來的12月9日至10日利率決策，他說：「我可以根據數據走向提出降息的理由，也可以提出維持利率不變的理由，我們拭目以待。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-900c45a3-94ac-3f9e-8258-66d26d21f27e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"明尼阿波利斯聯邦儲備銀行行長Neel Kashkari攝影：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Fbsy_9WTt6Ywqd2joOLhUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b88a8371020ed02cfde29ec6d6ceddc9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">明尼阿波利斯聯邦儲備銀行行長Neel Kashkari攝影：Victor J. Blue/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kashkari今年不參與利率決策的投票，但他會參與聯邦公開市場委員會的審議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Kashkari Didn’t Support Last Cut, Undecided on December</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83kashkari%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%8A%E6%AC%A1%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF-%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E5%B0%B112%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E6%8B%BF%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%84%8F-210237281.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 05:45:43",
