        {
            "title": "與美國部長看法迥異 滙豐高管指中國在AI所需能源上獨具優勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t4cG7O6bo7rU2SB.4q.z6Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cc1f5d049d23e3ab54a9938c4783a6c6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國在清潔能源領域的主導地位令其與別國、尤其是美國競爭時占據了極其有利的位置，包括人工智能領域。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這就是滙豐控股首席可持續發展官Julian Wentzel的看法。他認為，建立在可再生能源基礎上的經濟具有化石燃料無法復制的優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「中國在能源需求方面已經將自己帶到了一個非常獨特的地位，不僅能推動他們的經濟，最終也能有助於他們的人工智能架構，」  Wentzel在一次採訪中說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示，一旦可再生能源基礎設施建成且前期投資收回成本，生產額外能源實際上就不會產生任何更多的成本。Wentzel說，化石燃料恰恰相反，開采、運輸、提煉和分銷都需要持續投入。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cd6bb7e9-fe37-32ba-9f9c-d76b7313999d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他的看法與美國政府的政策立場截然相反。能源部長Chris Wright就曾表示，快速向清潔能源轉型會推高能源成本並損害經濟成長。而就目前而言，化石燃料仍然在為人工智能數據中心提供著大部分所需的能源。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"726\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VVOlsv1Op35bP.WDDcOzwQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyNjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7023c67480ade5f54ea5ca8a7608638e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wentzel還表示，更加依賴清潔能源的經濟體也更有可能降低通膨波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「減少對燃料商品的依賴可以降低資本賬戶波動、通膨風險和價格波動。隨著可再生能源系統規模的擴大，能源成本占GDP的比重可以下降，從而提高系統的財務效率，並支持更高的經濟增速，」 他說。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"607\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NJ0ySHIfuZIDxGECvPwhdw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/764e91684a6b22c84605b511c77d1032\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題HSBC Executive Says China ‘Uniquely’ Strong on AI Energy Supply</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Stephen Stapczynski.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
